headline: Fastenal (NasdaqGS:FAST) Declares US$0.22 Dividend Following Two-For-One Stock Split
summary: Fastenal (NasdaqGS:FAST) recently announced a dividend of $0.22 per share to be paid in August, following a two-for-one stock split effective in May 2025. Over the past quarter, Fastenal's stock price increased by 7%, aligning closely with the broader market's upward movement over the past year. The stock split and dividend declaration likely bolstered investor confidence, adding weight to Fastenal's performance.
